snippet.title: Fable Official Trailer | Xbox Games Showcase 2023
snippet.description:
Fable is finally back! After years away, one of Xbox's biggest Ips has returned. We see " Dave Vegetable Enthusiast" discussing the age of heroes is over, the age of innovation is here. Who, of course, turns out to be a giant.

#xbox #gaming #fable
